The Android Open Source Project (AOSP), an open source initiative by Google. The repository offer the information and source code needed to create custom variants of the Android OS, port devices and accessories to the Android platform which are also called Custom ROM.

Custom Rom is a modified version of pure Android source code. Many developers collaborate to build the fastest and features filled beautiful ROMs. There are a lot of custom ROMs available for many devices to try.

Many expert developers have ported the Google camera shipped with Pixel devices for other android devices. To use Gcam port, you need following pre-requisites.
* Camera2api enabled\n * GCam Port APK

You can customize your android device by installing launchers and icons packs. This can giv you some refreshed look to your device. And if you want some deep customization the you need to have root access of your device. Customizing your device include changing the look of your device as well as increasing performance and battery life for your device.There are some apps popular available.

* Magisk Manager
 * Substratum
 * FK Kernel Manager
 * Wakelock Detector
 * Xposed Framework
 * Apps2SD
 * Titanium Backup
 * Viper4Android
 * Tasker
 * Adblock Plus
